project_descr: Institutional and individual capacities developed towards promotion of Youth volunteerism

outputs.output_descr: The present project represents a unique partnership between an NGO (Warif) and the UNDP with the objective of increasing youth participation in the national development processes. Youth participation in development is perceived to sustain the national development results while ensuring that such development is inclusive and participatory in a meaningful way. The project is envisaged to compliment recent public-sector efforts, which are mainly UNDP-supported, to strategically approach issues of youth participation in development.
